# Snake Game Library

![Snake Game](snakegame/screenshot.png)

A simple Snake Game library for Python using Pygame.

## Installation

pip install ularkotak

## Usage

```python
from snakegame.game import SnakeGame

if __name__ == "__main__":
    game = SnakeGame()
    game.run()
```
